Package: libxrdp
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Architecture: ARCH
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: XRDP shared libraries
 XRDP is an open source remote desktop protocol(rdp) server.
 .
 This package provides XRDP shared libraries and modules.

Package: libxrdp-dev
Section: libdevel
Priority: optional
Architecture: ARCH
Provides: xrdp-dev (= ${binary:Version})
Depends: libxrdp (= ${binary:Version}), libfuse2-dev, libice-dev, 
 libjpeg-turbo-dev, libpam-dev, libpixman-dev, libsm-dev, 
 libx11-dev, libxfixes-dev, libxrandr-dev, openssl-dev
Description: XRDP development headers and static libraries
 This package provides XRDP static libraries, pkgconfig data 
 and header files required for developing applications which 
 use XRDP API routines.

