 This package provides the XRDP server and userspace tools.

Package: xrdp-doc
Section: doc
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Recommends: man-db
Depends: xrdp (= ${binary:Version})
Description: XRDP documentation
 This package provides manual pages for the XRDP server and
